(42, '2016-07-03 00:42:46', 'test', 'martin arn', 'pantanal@gmx.net', 'martin arn', '', 'martin arn', 14, '<html xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word" xmlns:m="http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/2004/12/omml" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40"><head><meta http-equiv=Content-Type content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name=Generator content="Microsoft Word 15 (filtered medium)"><style><!--\r\n/* Font Definitions */\r\n@font-face\r\n	{font-family:"Cambria Math";\r\n	panose-1:2 4 5 3 5 4 6 3 2 4;}\r\n@font-face\r\n	{font-family:Calibri;\r\n	panose-1:2 15 5 2 2 2 4 3 2 4;}\r\n/* Style Definitions */\r\np.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\r\n	{margin:0cm;\r\n	margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	font-size:11.0pt;\r\n	font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;}\r\n.MsoChpDefault\r\n	{mso-style-type:export-only;}\r\n@page WordSection1\r\n	{size:612.0pt 792.0pt;\r\n	margin:70.85pt 70.85pt 2.0cm 70.85pt;}\r\ndiv.WordSection1\r\n	{page:WordSection1;}\r\n--></style></head><body lang=DE-CH><div class=WordSection1><p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=MsoNormal>GoPantanal.com</p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></div></body></html>', 0),
(43, '2016-06-28 23:58:33', 'Re: AW: AW: Bonito em setembro', 'Marta Keppler', 'mmkeppler@gmail.com', 'martin arn', '', 'Marta Keppler', 15, '<p dir="ltr">Obrigada, vou conversar com meu marido. Tenho uma dúvida, todos passeios estão incluídos. Há ingressos para parques? Está tudo incluído?  Neste caso só providenciamos as passagens e as refeições mencionadas? </p>\r\n<div class="gmail_quote">Em 28 de jun de 2016 18:38, &quot;martin arn&quot; &lt;<a href="mailto:info@gopantanal.com">info@gopantanal.com</a>&gt; escreveu:<br type="attribution"><blockquote class="gmail_quote" style="margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex"><div lang="DE-CH" link="blue" vlink="#954F72"><div><p class="MsoNormal">Boa noite Marta,</p><p class="MsoNormal"><u></u> <u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal">segue em anexo a proposta de passeio para Bonito e Pantanal. </p><p class="MsoNormal"><u></u> <u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal">Quais quer perguntas ou desejos de mudanca na programacao podem ser respondidas. Sera um grande prazer de ajuda-los.</p><p class="MsoNormal"><u></u> <u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal">Atenciosamente</p><p class="MsoNormal"><u></u> <u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal">Martin Arn</p><p class="MsoNormal">GoPanatanal.com<u></u><u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal"><u></u> <u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal">Gesendet von <a href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=550986" target="_blank">Mail</a> für Windows 10</p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><u></u> <u></u></span></p><div style="border:none;border-top:solid #e1e1e1 1.0pt;padding:3.0pt 0cm 0cm 0cm"><p class="MsoNormal" style="border:none;padding:0cm"><b>Von: </b><a href="mailto:mmkeppler@gmail.com" target="_blank">Marta Keppler</a><br><b>Gesendet: </b>Samstag, 25. Juni 2016 16:56<br><b>An: </b><a href="mailto:info@gopantanal.com" target="_blank">martin arn</a><br><b>Betreff: </b>Re: AW: Bonito em setembro</p></div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><u></u> <u></u></span></p><p>Olá, sem problemas! Aguardo, obrigada</p><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Em 25 de jun de 2016 07:46, &quot;martin arn&quot; &lt;<a href="mailto:info@gopantanal.com" target="_blank">info@gopantanal.com</a>&gt; escreveu:<u></u><u></u></span></p><blockquote style="border:none;border-left:solid #cccccc 1.0pt;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 6.0pt;margin-left:4.8pt;margin-right:0cm"><div><div><p class="MsoNormal">Bom dia Marta,<u></u><u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal"> </p><p class="MsoNormal">chegarei amanha em casa e te envio ao maximo ate terca feira umas propostas detailhadas.</p><p class="MsoNormal"> </p><p class="MsoNormal">Obrigado pela paciencia.</p><p class="MsoNormal"> </p><p class="MsoNormal">Atenciosamente</p><p class="MsoNormal"> </p><p class="MsoNormal">Martin Arn</p><p class="MsoNormal"> </p><p class="MsoNormal">Gesendet von <a href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=550986" target="_blank">Mail</a> für Windows 10</p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"> </span></p><div style="border:none;border-top:solid #e1e1e1 1.0pt;padding:3.0pt 0cm 0cm 0cm"><p class="MsoNormal"><b>Von: </b><a href="mailto:mmkeppler@gmail.com" target="_blank">Marta Keppler</a><br><b>Gesendet: </b>Sonntag, 19. Juni 2016 13:59<br><b>An: </b><a href="mailto:info@gopantanal.com" target="_blank">martin arn</a><br><b>Betreff: </b>Re: Bonito em setembro</p></div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"> </span></p><div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Olá</span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Meu marido tem 64 e eu 58 anos. Dependendo do preço podemos fazer Bonito e Pantanal, podemos dispor de até uns 8 ou 9 dias se for os 2 roteiros. </span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Quanto aos passeios não queremos fazer nada muito radical e as caminhadas podem até ser longas, mas nível fácil, pois meu marido tem problema no joelho. De resto gostamos de tudo, por favor mande a proposta e vamos acertando o que gostamos mais. Seu pacote inclui tudo ou só os passeios?</span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Marta</span></p></div></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"> </span></p><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Em 19 de junho de 2016 07:51, martin arn &lt;<a href="mailto:info@gopantanal.com" target="_blank">info@gopantanal.com</a>&gt; escreveu:</span></p><blockquote style="border:none;border-left:solid #cccccc 1.0pt;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 6.0pt;margin-left:4.8pt;margin-top:5.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:5.0pt"><div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="PT-BR">Bom dia Marta,</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="PT-BR"> </span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="PT-BR">obrigado pelo contato. Com muito prazer  monto um pacote para voce. </span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="PT-BR"> </span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="PT-BR">Para te atender melhor me ajudariam receber algumas informacoes a mais. </span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="PT-BR"> </span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="PT-BR">Sua idade, quantos dias, somente Bonito ou tambem Pantanal que esta ao lado, preferencias de passeios (grutas, flutuacao, caminhadas, cachoeiras, atividades radicais,) animais que gostaria de ver</span>.</p><p class="MsoNormal"> </p><p class="MsoNormal">O<span lang="PT-BR">bservacao: Estarei nos proximos dias no Pantanal, Sem acesso ao Internet. Assim que puder te farei a oferta.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="PT-BR"> </span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="PT-BR">Atenciosamente</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"> </p><p class="MsoNormal">Martin Arn</p><p class="MsoNormal">GoPantanal.com</p><p class="MsoNormal"> </p><p class="MsoNormal"> </p><p class="MsoNormal"> </p><p class="MsoNormal">Gesendet von <a href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=550986" target="_blank">Mail</a> für Windows 10</p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"> </span></p></div></div></blockquote></div></div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"> </span></p></div></div></blockquote></div><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:4.8pt"> </p><p class="MsoNormal"><u></u> <u></u></p></div></div></blockquote></div>\r\n', 0),
(44, '2016-06-26 17:52:11', 'Re: AW: AW: AW: Tour pantanal', 'dominik bausinger', 'dbwau@gmx.net', 'martin arn', '', 'dominik bausinger', 16, '<html><head></head><body style="word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; ">Hallo Martin,<div>nochmal ich,</div><div>alles klar,</div><div>ging ohne BIC.</div><div>Bis in B?lde!</div><div>Dominik</div><div><br></div><div><div><div>Am 26.06.2016 um 17:39 schrieb dominik bausinger:</div><br class="Apple-interchange-newline"><blockquote type="cite"><div style="word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; ">Guten Abend Martin,<div><br></div><div>irgendwie klappt das mit dem ?berweisen nicht...</div><div>Die BIC sei nicht korrekt,</div><div>sagt das Schaltfeld...</div><div>Bitte schau doch nochmal, ob da was falsch ist...</div><div><br></div><div>Viele liebe Gr??e!</div><div>Dominik</div><div><br></div><div><br><div><div>Am 25.06.2016 um 11:54 schrieb martin arn:</div><br class="Apple-interchange-newline"><blockquote type="cite"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="Generator" content="Microsoft Word 15 (filtered medium)"><style><!--\r\n/* Font Definitions */\r\n@font-face\r\n	{font-family:"Cambria Math";\r\n	panose-1:2 4 5 3 5 4 6 3 2 4;}\r\n@font-face\r\n	{font-family:Calibri;\r\n	panose-1:2 15 5 2 2 2 4 3 2 4;}\r\n/* Style Definitions */\r\np.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\r\n	{margin:0cm;\r\n	margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	font-size:11.0pt;\r\n	font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;}\r\na:link, span.MsoHyperlink\r\n	{mso-style-priority:99;\r\n	color:blue;\r\n	text-decoration:underline;}\r\na:visited, span.MsoHyperlinkFollowed\r\n	{mso-style-priority:99;\r\n	color:#954F72;\r\n	text-decoration:underline;}\r\n.MsoChpDefault\r\n	{mso-style-type:export-only;}\r\n@page WordSection1\r\n	{size:612.0pt 792.0pt;\r\n	margin:70.85pt 70.85pt 2.0cm 70.85pt;}\r\ndiv.WordSection1\r\n	{page:WordSection1;}\r\n--></style><div lang="DE-CH" link="blue" vlink="#954F72"><div class="WordSection1"><p class="MsoNormal">Guten Tag Dominik,</p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">sorry meinerseits fuer die spaete Antwort. War ganz tief im Pantanal ohne Tel und Internetzugang.</p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">Gerne hole ich euch am 4.7. auf dem Flughafen ab und bringe euch zu uns wo ihr in unserem Gaestezimmer uerbernachten koennt. Fuer die Uebernachtung vom 9.7.-10.7. bitte ich euch im Hotel zu uebernachten. Meine Frau hatte eine schwere Operation und da ich ab 7.7. wieder unterwegs bin moechte ich ihr die Mehrarbeit nicht zumuten. Das Hostel Vitoria Regia und das Hotel Mohave befinden sich in der Naehe des Flughafens. Ein Taxi von dort kostet weniger als 10 Euro.</p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">Hier noch die Bankdaten fuer die Ueberweisung</p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">Bank. Postfinance</p><p class="MsoNormal">Kontonummer 25-546648-6</p><p class="MsoNormal">IBAN CH5609000000255466486</p><p class="MsoNormal">BIC BLZ POFICHBEXX</p><p class="MsoNormal">Martin Arn</p><p class="MsoNormal">Riedhofstrasse 366</p><p class="MsoNormal">8049 Zuerich</p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">Die restlichen 70% vorzugsweise in bar in bras Waehrung. Wenn nicht moeglich, kann notfalls auf er Lodge mit Kreditkarte bezahlt werden.</p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">Wichtig: 1 Satz warme Kleider mitnehmen. Juli ist Wintermonat mit Temperaturen bis um die 10 Grad.</p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">Mit besten Gruessen Martin Arn</p><p class="MsoNormal"><a href="http://GoPantanal.com/">GoPantanal.com</a></p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">Gesendet von <a href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=550986">Mail</a> f?r Windows 10</p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><div style="mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-top:solid #E1E1E1 1.0pt;padding:3.0pt 0cm 0cm 0cm"><p class="MsoNormal" style="border:none;padding:0cm"><b>Von: </b><a href="mailto:dbwau@gmx.net">Dominik Bausinger</a><br><b>Gesendet: </b>Mittwoch, 22. Juni 2016 15:18<br><b>An: </b><a href="mailto:info@gopantanal.com">martin arn</a><br><b>Betreff: </b>Re: AW: AW: Tour pantanal</p></div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Hallo Martin,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><o:p></o:p></span></p><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Sorry, dass es so lange gedauert hat.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Jedenfalls haben wir uns entschieden die Tour zu buchen und freuen uns schon sehr!<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Da wir fr?hestens am 4.7. am sp?ten Nachmittag ankommen werden, wird es leider nur die k?rzere Variante werden.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Wahrscheinlich w?rden wir in Euer guesthouse gehen, sowohl vom 4. auf den 5., als auch vom 9. auf den 10.7.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">W?re das m?glich? Wie s?he es mit abholen und bringen vom/zum Flughafen aus?<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Und ganz wichtig, kannst Du mir eine Kontonummer geben, dass ich zumindest schonmal einen Teil der Reise anzahle?<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Oder ist es mit Kreditkarte besser?<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Fragen ?ber Fragen,&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">freu mich, von Dir zu h?ren,<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Herzliche Gr??e aus einen sehr hei?en Berlin,<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Dominik<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><br>Von meinem iPhone gesendet<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:12.0pt"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><br>Am 16.06.2016 um 04:18 schrieb martin arn &lt;<a href="mailto:info@gopantanal.com">info@gopantanal.com</a>&gt;:<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><blockquote style="margin-top:5.0pt;margin-bottom:5.0pt"><div><p class="MsoNormal">Hallo Dominik,<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">sorry, dass es etwas l?nger gedauert hat. Ich musste die Ausfl?ge in Bonito noch abkl?ren. Im Juli ist hier Ferienzeit und praktisch alle guten Ausfl?ge ausgebucht. Es hat aber geklappt euch noch einzubinden.</p><p class="MsoNormal">Ich habe dir im Anhang einen Tourvorschlag zugesandt, welcher eine zus?tzliche Option (in Rot) enth?lt. </p><p class="MsoNormal">Wenn ihr Option rot w?hlt , m?sst ihr die Tour am 4. Juli starten, ansonsten am 5. Juli. </p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Da ist eine Budgetour mit upgrade, dh. Privates Doppelzimmer und bessere Unterkunft und Ausfl?ge in Bonito.</p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Selbstverst?ndlich stehe ich dir f?r s?mtliche Fragen gerne zur Verf?gung</p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Mit besten Gr?ssen</p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Martin Arn</p><p class="MsoNormal"><a href="http://gopantanal.com/">GoPantanal.com</a>.</p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Gesendet von <a href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=550986">Mail</a> f?r Windows 10</p><div><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">&nbsp;</span><br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><div style="border:none;border-top:solid #E1E1E1 1.0pt;padding:3.0pt 0cm 0cm 0cm"><p class="MsoNormal"><b>Von: </b><a href="mailto:dbwau@gmx.net">Dominik Bausinger</a><br><b>Gesendet: </b>Dienstag, 14. Juni 2016 12:13<br><b>An: </b><a href="mailto:info@gopantanal.com">martin arn</a><br><b>Betreff: </b>Re: AW: Tour pantanal</p></div><div><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">&nbsp;</span><br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Vielen Dank schonmal!</span></p><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Freu mich!</span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><br><br>Von meinem iPhone gesendet</span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:12.0pt"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><br>Am 14.06.2016 um 17:54 schrieb martin arn &lt;<a href="mailto:info@gopantanal.com">info@gopantanal.com</a>&gt;:</span></p></div><blockquote style="margin-top:5.0pt;margin-bottom:5.0pt"><div><p class="MsoNormal">Hallo Dominik, </p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">vielen Dank fuer deine Anfrage.</p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Ich werde dir bis morgen einen auf euch zugeschnittenen Tourvorschlag zusenden.</p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Mit besten Gruessen</p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Martin Arn</p><p class="MsoNormal"><a href="http://gopantanal.com/">GoPantanal.com</a></p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Gesendet von <a href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=550986">Mail</a> f?r Windows 10</p><div><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">&nbsp;</span><br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><div style="border:none;border-top:solid #E1E1E1 1.0pt;padding:3.0pt 0cm 0cm 0cm"><p class="MsoNormal"><b>Von: </b><a href="mailto:dbwau@gmx.net">Dominik Bausinger</a><br><b>Gesendet: </b>Dienstag, 14. Juni 2016 10:42<br><b>An: </b><a href="mailto:info@gopantanal.com">info@gopantanal.com</a><br><b>Cc: </b><a href="mailto:pantanal@gmx.net">pantanal@gmx.net</a><br><b>Betreff: </b>Tour pantanal</p></div><div><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">&nbsp;</span><br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Lieber Martin,</p><p class="MsoNormal">beim durchforsten von allm?hlichen Angeboten f?r Touren ins pantanal, ist mir Eure Seite erfreulich aufgefallen...</p><p class="MsoNormal">Ich hole Ende Juni meine Tochter Leika, 16, von ihrem Auslandsjahr in Brasilien ab, und wir planen noch ein bisschen gemeinsam ein paar Ecken von Brasilien zu erkunden. Fest vorgenommen haben wir uns eine Tour ins pantanal, ggf. auch bonito..</p><p class="MsoNormal">Es w?re toll, Du k?nntest uns ein Angebot machen, bzw. vielleicht mehrere zur Auswahl. </p><p class="MsoNormal">Eckdaten: ab 4. oder 5.7. f?r drei bis f?nf n?chte...</p><p class="MsoNormal">Leider kein riesiges Budget vorhanden, aber ein bisschen was geht schon. Auf jeden Fall sind wir sehr interessiert und voll der Vorfreude!</p><p class="MsoNormal">Freuen uns auf Deine antwort, herzliche Gr??e aus Berlin,</p><p class="MsoNormal">Dominik</p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Von meinem iPhone gesendet</p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div></div></blockquote><div style="margin-right: 36pt; margin-bottom: 5pt; margin-left: 36pt; ">&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div></div></blockquote><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt:5.0pt;margin-right:36.0pt;margin-bottom:5.0pt;margin-left:36.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">&lt;Dominik Bausinger.docx&gt;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p></div></div></blockquote></div><br></div></div></blockquote></div><br></div></body></html>', 0);
