al">Wenn ihr Option rot w?hlt , m?sst ihr die Tour am 4. Juli starten, ansonsten am 5. Juli. </p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Da ist eine Budgetour mit upgrade, dh. Privates Doppelzimmer und bessere Unterkunft und Ausfl?ge in Bonito.</p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Selbstverst?ndlich stehe ich dir f?r s?mtliche Fragen gerne zur Verf?gung</p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Mit besten Gr?ssen</p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Martin Arn</p><p class="MsoNormal"><a href="http://gopantanal.com/">GoPantanal.com</a>.</p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Gesendet von <a href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=550986">Mail</a> f?r Windows 10</p><div><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">&nbsp;</span><br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><div style="border:none;border-top:solid #E1E1E1 1.0pt;padding:3.0pt 0cm 0cm 0cm"><p class="MsoNormal"><b>Von: </b><a href="mailto:dbwau@gmx.net">Dominik Bausinger</a><br><b>Gesendet: </b>Dienstag, 14. Juni 2016 12:13<br><b>An: </b><a href="mailto:info@gopantanal.com">martin arn</a><br><b>Betreff: </b>Re: AW: Tour pantanal</p></div><div><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">&nbsp;</span><br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Vielen Dank schonmal!</span></p><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Freu mich!</span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><br><br>Von meinem iPhone gesendet</span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:12.0pt"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><br>Am 14.06.2016 um 17:54 schrieb martin arn &lt;<a href="mailto:info@gopantanal.com">info@gopantanal.com</a>&gt;:</span></p></div><blockquote style="margin-top:5.0pt;margin-bottom:5.0pt"><div><p class="MsoNormal">Hallo Dominik, </p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">vielen Dank fuer deine Anfrage.</p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Ich werde dir bis morgen einen auf euch zugeschnittenen Tourvorschlag zusenden.</p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Mit besten Gruessen</p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Martin Arn</p><p class="MsoNormal"><a href="http://gopantanal.com/">GoPantanal.com</a></p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Gesendet von <a href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=550986">Mail</a> f?r Windows 10</p><div><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">&nbsp;</span><br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><div style="border:none;border-top:solid #E1E1E1 1.0pt;padding:3.0pt 0cm 0cm 0cm"><p class="MsoNormal"><b>Von: </b><a href="mailto:dbwau@gmx.net">Dominik Bausinger</a><br><b>Gesendet: </b>Dienstag, 14. Juni 2016 10:42<br><b>An: </b><a href="mailto:info@gopantanal.com">info@gopantanal.com</a><br><b>Cc: </b><a href="mailto:pantanal@gmx.net">pantanal@gmx.net</a><br><b>Betreff: </b>Tour pantanal</p></div><div><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">&nbsp;</span><br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Lieber Martin,</p><p class="MsoNormal">beim durchforsten von allm?hlichen Angeboten f?r Touren ins pantanal, ist mir Eure Seite erfreulich aufgefallen...</p><p class="MsoNormal">Ich hole Ende Juni meine Tochter Leika, 16, von ihrem Auslandsjahr in Brasilien ab, und wir planen noch ein bisschen gemeinsam ein paar Ecken von Brasilien zu erkunden. Fest vorgenommen haben wir uns eine Tour ins pantanal, ggf. auch bonito..</p><p class="MsoNormal">Es w?re toll, Du k?nntest uns ein Angebot machen, bzw. vielleicht mehrere zur Auswahl. </p><p class="MsoNormal">Eckdaten: ab 4. oder 5.7. f?r drei bis f?nf n?chte...</p><p class="MsoNormal">Leider kein riesiges Budget vorhanden, aber ein bisschen was geht schon. Auf jeden Fall sind wir sehr interessiert und voll der Vorfreude!</p><p class="MsoNormal">Freuen uns auf Deine antwort, herzliche Gr??e aus Berlin,</p><p class="MsoNormal">Dominik</p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><p class="MsoNormal">Von meinem iPhone gesendet</p><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div></div></blockquote><div style="margin-right: 36pt; margin-bottom: 5pt; margin-left: 36pt; ">&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div><div>&nbsp;<br class="webkit-block-placeholder"></div></div></blockquote><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt:5.0pt;margin-right:36.0pt;margin-bottom:5.0pt;margin-left:36.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">&lt;Dominik Bausinger.docx&gt;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p></div></div></blockquote></div><br></div></body></html>', 0),
(46, '2016-06-26 01:01:47', 'Re: Reserve GoPantanal Martin', 'Reserva Hotel MoHave', 'reserva@hotelmohave.com.br', 'martin arnReserva Hotel MoHaverecepcaomohave@hotmail.com', '', 'Reserva Hotel MoHave', 18, '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=us-ascii">\r\n</head>\r\n<body dir="auto">\r\n<div>Boa noite,</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Reserva confirmada<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCARLOS VARGAS</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nEm 25/06/2016, &agrave;s 06:59 PM, &quot;martin arn&quot; &lt;<a href="mailto:info@gopantanal.com">info@gopantanal.com</a>&gt; escreveu:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<blockquote type="cite">\r\n<div>\r\n<meta name="Generator" content="Microsoft Word 15 (filtered medium)">\r\n<style><!--\r\n/* Font Definitions */\r\n@font-face\r\n	{font-family:"Cambria Math";\r\n	panose-1:2 4 5 3 5 4 6 3 2 4;}\r\n@font-face\r\n	{font-family:Calibri;\r\n	panose-1:2 15 5 2 2 2 4 3 2 4;}\r\n/* Style Definitions */\r\np.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\r\n	{margin:0cm;\r\n	margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	font-size:11.0pt;\r\n	font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;}\r\na:link, span.MsoHyperlink\r\n	{mso-style-priority:99;\r\n	color:blue;\r\n	text-decoration:underline;}\r\na:visited, span.MsoHyperlinkFollowed\r\n	{mso-style-priority:99;\r\n	color:#954F72;\r\n	text-decoration:underline;}\r\n.MsoChpDefault\r\n	{mso-style-type:export-only;}\r\n@page WordSection1\r\n	{size:612.0pt 792.0pt;\r\n	margin:70.85pt 70.85pt 2.0cm 70.85pt;}\r\ndiv.WordSection1\r\n	{page:WordSection1;}\r\n--></style>\r\n<div class="WordSection1">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Boa noite,</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Como conversei ontem por telefone gostaria de confirmar a reserva para</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Apartamento duplo (casal) check in 26.6.&nbsp; pelas 21hs</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Check out 27.6. pelas 9hs</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Em nome de Claudia Diederich e Ralf Boenig.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Obs. O pagamento sera feito pelos proprios hospedes</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Atenciosamente</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Martin Arn<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Gesendet von <a href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=550986">\r\nMail</a> f&uuml;r Windows 10</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', 0),
(47, '2016-06-25 22:56:07', 'Re: AW: Bonito em setembro', 'Marta Keppler', 'mmkeppler@gmail.com', 'martin arn', '', 'Marta Keppler', 19, '<p dir="ltr">Olá, sem problemas! Aguardo, obrigada</p>\r\n<div class="gmail_quote">Em 25 de jun de 2016 07:46, &quot;martin arn&quot; &lt;<a href="mailto:info@gopantanal.com">info@gopantanal.com</a>&gt; escreveu:<br type="attribution"><blockquote class="gmail_quote" style="margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex"><div lang="DE-CH" link="blue" vlink="#954F72"><div><p class="MsoNormal">Bom dia Marta,</p><p class="MsoNormal"><u></u> <u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal">chegarei amanha em casa e te envio ao maximo ate terca feira umas propostas detailhadas.</p><p class="MsoNormal"><u></u> <u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal">Obrigado pela paciencia.</p><p class="MsoNormal"><u></u> <u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal">Atenciosamente</p><p class="MsoNormal"><u></u> <u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal">Martin Arn<u></u><u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal"><u></u> <u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal">Gesendet von <a href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=550986" target="_blank">Mail</a> für Windows 10</p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><u></u> <u></u></span></p><div style="border:none;border-top:solid #e1e1e1 1.0pt;padding:3.0pt 0cm 0cm 0cm"><p class="MsoNormal" style="border:none;padding:0cm"><b>Von: </b><a href="mailto:mmkeppler@gmail.com" target="_blank">Marta Keppler</a><br><b>Gesendet: </b>Sonntag, 19. Juni 2016 13:59<br><b>An: </b><a href="mailto:info@gopantanal.com" target="_blank">martin arn</a><br><b>Betreff: </b>Re: Bonito em setembro</p></div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><u></u> <u></u></span></p><div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Olá</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><u></u><u></u></span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Meu marido tem 64 e eu 58 anos. Dependendo do preço podemos fazer Bonito e Pantanal, podemos dispor de até uns 8 ou 9 dias se for os 2 roteiros. <u></u><u></u></span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Quanto aos passeios não queremos fazer nada muito radical e as caminhadas podem até ser longas, mas nível fácil, pois meu marido tem problema no joelho. De resto gostamos de tudo, por favor mande a proposta e vamos acertando o que gostamos mais. Seu pacote inclui tudo ou só os passeios?<u></u><u></u></span></p></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Marta<u></u><u></u></span></p></div></div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><u></u> <u></u></span></p><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Em 19 de junho de 2016 07:51, martin arn &lt;<a href="mailto:info@gopantanal.com" target="_blank">info@gopantanal.com</a>&gt; escreveu:<u></u><u></u></span></p><blockquote style="border:none;border-left:solid #cccccc 1.0pt;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 6.0pt;margin-left:4.8pt;margin-right:0cm"><div><div><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="PT-BR">Bom dia Marta,</span><u></u><u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="PT-BR"> </span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="PT-BR">obrigado pelo contato. Com muito prazer  monto um pacote para voce. </span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="PT-BR"> </span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="PT-BR">Para te atender melhor me ajudariam receber algumas informacoes a mais. </span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="PT-BR"> </span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="PT-BR">Sua idade, quantos dias, somente Bonito ou tambem Pantanal que esta ao lado, preferencias de passeios (grutas, flutuacao, caminhadas, cachoeiras, atividades radicais,) animais que gostaria de ver</span>.</p><p class="MsoNormal"> </p><p class="MsoNormal">O<span lang="PT-BR">bservacao: Estarei nos proximos dias no Pantanal, Sem acesso ao Internet. Assim que puder te farei a oferta.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="PT-BR"> </span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="PT-BR">Atenciosamente</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"> </p><p class="MsoNormal">Martin Arn</p><p class="MsoNormal">GoPantanal.com</p><p class="MsoNormal"> </p><p class="MsoNormal"> </p><p class="MsoNormal"> </p><p class="MsoNormal">Gesendet von <a href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=550986" target="_blank">Mail</a> für Windows 10</p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"> </span></p></div></div></blockquote></div></div><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><u></u> <u></u></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><u></u> <u></u></p></div></div></blockquote></div>\r\n', 0),
